data.description: Location! Location! Location! Huge Price Improvement! Motived seller!  Bring your offer! Welcome to this beautiful 3 beadrooms and 1.5 bathrooms home in one of the best location in Atlanta. This recently renovated 2-story condominium is located in Atlanta's perimeter where easy commute to Atlanta's top schools/universities (Mercer, Emory, GA Tech, GA State) and is very convinence to travel Downtown Atlanta, CDC, Midtown Atlant, Airport. Easy access to public transportation, highways (I-85, I-285) shooping, resturants and parks. This home has been recently updated and is  Move-In ready. New paint, new flooring etc. HVAC system was replaced couple years ago. All appliances will stay with the home. Priced to sell! No waits, call your agent to schedule a showing today.
